Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.04,0:00:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That was because my brother and I
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.00,0:00:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,weren't born with any power.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.29,0:00:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We were Bell Peppers.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.83,0:00:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Alice...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.88,0:00:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.71,0:00:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Alice...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.17,0:00:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,He traveled back in time
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.25,0:00:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,to alter Alice's destiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.54,0:00:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We can stop Togetsu's mainframe,\NBABE, from functioning.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.04,0:00:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,How does that sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.92,0:00:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The researches on Red Strings
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.88,0:00:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,and their plans of operations are all in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.79,0:00:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito, before we set out for Togetsu,\NI need to have a word with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.33,0:00:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,A word with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.75,0:01:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's not talk about it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.13,0:01:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We should talk outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.75,0:01:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Since everyone is present,\Nyou should listen to it too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.96,0:01:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this about?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.33,0:01:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.33,0:01:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's about Chairman Sumeragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.63,0:01:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,My father?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.25,0:01:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The man who killed him
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.25,0:01:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,was me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.88,0:01:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Kagero...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.29,0:01:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Kagero, now is not the time\Nfor one of your jokes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.75,0:01:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I think he is serious about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.58,0:01:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Kagero...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.21,0:02:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,SCARLET NEXUS
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.00,0:02:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Felling of tiredness is losing yourself♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.04,0:02:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,♫How do you still create\Na relationship each other♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.25,0:02:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,♫It's my awkward friend's fault♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.17,0:02:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Until death, wanting someone\Nsomewhere to embrace me♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.50,0:02:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,♫While the devil is not here\Nand between the chaos♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.04,0:02:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Aiming between win and lose♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.38,0:02:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Not to be running out of patience for now,\NI'm trying to be careful♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.08,0:02:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,♫You'll see I'm always on your side♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.17,0:02:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,♫I tried hard to connect today as well♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.79,0:02:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,♫You're frigid and your roller coaster\Ninside the brain♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.25,0:02:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,♫The grungy days and\Nthe unprecedented catastrophy♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.71,0:02:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Where is the glory buried?♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.04,0:03:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,♫The lonely monster in a moment♫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.46,0:03:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,♫The bullet shot by the machinegun\Ngoes parallelly♫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.79,0:03:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,♫To pierce with the theory♫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.21,0:03:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,♫I tried hard to connect today as well♫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.29,0:03:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,♫The bullet shot by the machinegun\Ngoes parallelly♫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.38,0:03:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,♫I tried hard to connect today as well♫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.88,0:03:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,♫You're frigid and the theory in the brain♫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.92,0:03:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,"KAGERO'S CONFESSION"\NKagero, what are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.67,0:03:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you, I was a spy from Togetsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.83,0:03:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Chairman Sumeragi didn't trust Togetsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.17,0:03:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't know all the secrets\Nabout the Red Strings.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.75,0:03:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But he seemed to have noticed Togetsu's plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.58,0:03:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,So Togetsu saw the Chairman as a threat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.83,0:03:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.38,0:03:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That was why I was sent to Suoh
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.71,0:03:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,to join the OSF
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.38,0:04:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,so I could assassinate him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.92,0:04:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you wanted to stop Togetsu's plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.58,0:04:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. That is the reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.88,0:04:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't let the people from Togetsu\Nto question my loyalty.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.08,0:04:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I had to follow their orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.92,0:04:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't personally hate the Chairman.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.25,0:04:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But I had to do it for my own sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.33,0:04:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,To simply put, I was
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.83,0:04:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,saving my own skin.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.46,0:04:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, what are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.25,0:04:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane, you were there too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.21,0:04:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I think the Chairman told you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.92,0:04:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,"He was in the OSF."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.88,0:04:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,"He's a spy from Togetsu."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.08,0:04:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I am the spy he spoke of.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.75,0:04:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,And then the Chairman told
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.79,0:04:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,to leave him behind and get to shelter.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.96,0:04:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,OSF...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.83,0:04:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Togetsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.88,0:05:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave me behind. Get to shelter.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.00,0:05:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, he said that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.42,0:05:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito arrived soon after.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.25,0:05:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,-That means...\N-So Kagero, it was your doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.21,0:05:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. You got it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.75,0:05:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it true?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.75,0:05:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you really do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.08,0:05:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Weren't you listening to me at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.21,0:05:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.63,0:05:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you bring it up now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.83,0:05:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm apologizing to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.58,0:05:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Does the reason really matter now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.25,0:05:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Although I know for certain\Nyou wouldn't forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.71,0:05:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What will you do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.54,0:05:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want me to be gone for good,\NI'll respect your decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.42,0:05:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this how you see it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.50,0:05:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.63,0:05:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,This is exactly who I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.71,0:05:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, I shall put an end to this my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.08,0:05:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.25,0:05:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, you can't be serious about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.92,0:05:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Young Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.13,0:06:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you really want a fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.71,0:06:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Fight me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.29,0:06:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm dead serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.83,0:06:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito, Kagero, stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.42,0:06:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave them be.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.08,0:06:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.25,0:06:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,They will never move on unless they fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.96,0:06:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,This is boring.\NWake me up when the fight is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.17,0:06:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,A spoiled young master like you\Nwould actually dare to fight me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.21,0:06:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You are no match for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.25,0:06:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.75,0:07:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't stay focused.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.71,0:07:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito, your power...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.13,0:07:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,This kid is really trying to take my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.50,0:07:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you kidding me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.54,0:07:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't die just yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.75,0:07:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Yuito! You can't kill me just yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.63,0:07:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.83,0:07:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Yuito!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.92,0:07:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,If I die now...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.42,0:07:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,two thousand years' worth of effort
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.08,0:07:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,will go down the drain if I die now!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.21,0:08:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You finally told me the truth, Kagero.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.67,0:08:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.67,0:08:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.17,0:08:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You wouldn't tell me the truth\Nunless I get serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.42,0:08:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Unbelievable.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.88,0:08:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't told me the whole story.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.83,0:08:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,-This way!\N-Please come here immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.17,0:08:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Regroup in Seiran!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.29,0:08:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Together, we will punish
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.33,0:08:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,New Himuka's system!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.46,0:08:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.13,0:09:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you a soldier of OSF?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.21,0:09:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Perfect timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.29,0:09:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,-Thank you.\N-Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.42,0:09:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too early to thank me,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.33,0:09:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Chairman Jo Sumeragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.58,0:09:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you with the rebels?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.17,0:09:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.42,0:09:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But Seiran's attack on Suoh created\Nthe perfect opening for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.46,0:09:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I should thank Karen and his rebels for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.25,0:09:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. You work for Togetsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.29,0:09:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.00,0:09:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,If you wanted me dead,\Nwhy would you save me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.67,0:09:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I have my own agenda.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.63,0:09:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell Togetsu you've been eliminated.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.58,0:09:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Please go into hiding for the time being.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.04,0:09:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll provide you with shelter.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.54,0:09:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you betraying Togetsu? But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.13,0:09:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,As I said, I have my own agenda.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.00,0:09:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.71,0:09:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I refuse the offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.29,0:09:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,New Himuka is in chaos.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.63,0:10:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,As a Sumeragi, I cannot forsake my people.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.21,0:10:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I spare you,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.71,0:10:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Togetsu will still come after you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.67,0:10:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You still have two amazing sons.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.25,0:10:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The rising star of OSF,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.46,0:10:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito Sumeragi
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.13,0:10:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,and Chief Kaito Sumeragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.71,0:10:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Your job will be a lot easier\Nif you let them handle some of the work.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.46,0:10:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You must already know what my family has done.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.17,0:10:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito is still unaware of the secrets\Nour family and this country is hiding.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.33,0:10:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaito misinterpreted\NYakumo Sumeragi's intention.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.88,0:10:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yakumo would never want a war to break out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.33,0:10:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The actions of the Sumeragi family\Nand New Himuka cannot be forgiven
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.54,0:10:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,even for the sake of\Nmaintaining peace and harmony.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.96,0:11:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,This is why I cannot go into hiding\Nor let myself get killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.83,0:11:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't just want to save the country,\NI want to correct all the sins it's committed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.25,0:11:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I want my sons to inherit my legacy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.17,0:11:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You turned out to be more righteous\Nthan I had anticipated.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.96,0:11:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like the other ancestors.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.58,0:11:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's harder to kill you now\Nthat you've mentioned that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.46,0:11:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But I need you to come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.58,0:11:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Back down!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.00,0:11:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.63,0:11:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Chairman Sumeragi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.46,0:11:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Chairman Sumeragi! Hang in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.71,0:12:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going to correct\Nthe wrongs of this country?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.46,0:12:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.63,0:12:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't killed him myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.29,0:12:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But he died right after\Nthe conversation was over.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.21,0:12:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I might as well have done so.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.08,0:12:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why you wanted to return\Nto Togetsu and finish the job.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.67,0:12:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You were merely trying to provoke us just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.92,0:12:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't mind if I died by Yuito's blade.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.92,0:12:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But to spill the truth in the end...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.00,0:12:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.08,0:12:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Before I put an end to Togetsu's plan,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.00,0:12:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't die.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.79,0:12:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsugumi, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.17,0:12:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You mentioned something about a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.50,0:12:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You mentioned it when we were in Togetsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.63,0:13:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Your family is still on the Moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.08,0:13:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.75,0:13:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it's my daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.67,0:13:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,My wife and daughter are on the Moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.13,0:13:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,If history is rewritten,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.92,0:13:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,my daughter will cease to exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.13,0:13:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't allow that to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.08,0:13:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't let Togetsu get their\Nhands on the Red Strings.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.42,0:13:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been 2000 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.63,0:13:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,They probably passed away.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.17,0:13:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You might think I am a fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.21,0:13:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But for me,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.17,0:13:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,my family and daughter still exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.75,0:13:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,My father used his power as the chairman\Nto stop the country's wrongdoing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.75,0:13:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,My father may have indirectly\Ncaused Nagi and Naomi's death.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.92,0:13:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But for me, he is still my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.13,0:14:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,This is why I can understand\Nwhy you want to your family to exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.83,0:14:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,When I lost my memories in Arahabaki,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.96,0:14:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I was terrified.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.88,0:14:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I lost myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.79,0:14:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want anyone else to feel the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.54,0:14:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone needs their past and memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.04,0:14:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We must stop Togetsu's plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.00,0:14:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I still can't forgive Kagero,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.54,0:14:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,but I think I'll have no problem\Nfighting Togetsu by your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.46,0:14:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You are much more mature than I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.88,0:14:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,No. It was me who acted like a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.29,0:14:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,In the end, you realized the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.21,0:14:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,How embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.83,0:14:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito, let me assist you on your way\Nto stop Togetsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.67,0:14:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.46,0:15:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.58,0:15:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That vibration was no normal earthquake.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.29,0:15:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. It was quite similar to the earthquake\Nwe encountered on the Kunad Highway.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.42,0:15:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Is everyone all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.46,0:15:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,There has been some anomaly with the Kunad Gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.29,0:15:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The whole New Himuka could feel the earthquake.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.33,0:15:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,There have been no casualties so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.96,0:15:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,We are safe too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.83,0:16:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,There hasn't been an avalanche\Nat the mountain either.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.29,0:16:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Does it mean the Kunad Gate has grown larger?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.67,0:16:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The gate is being maintained by my power.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.79,0:16:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The gate will disappear after I die.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.79,0:16:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That is the only way for\Nthe gate to be eliminated.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.38,0:16:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it because of my power?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.25,0:16:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Togetsu must have some researches\Nregarding the Kunad Gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.50,0:16:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. While we are stopping BABE,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.33,0:16:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,we could dig up some useful information.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.83,0:16:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We could even find a better plan there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.13,0:16:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.96,0:16:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,How is your power lately?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.04,0:16:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you feel discomfort when you use your power?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.21,0:16:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.25,0:16:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,After I was saved by all of you in Arahabaki,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.71,0:16:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,the headache stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.08,0:16:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.17,0:17:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad to hear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.17,0:17:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,When I was fighting you,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.33,0:17:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,how do I put it...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.88,0:17:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I could sense the abnormal power surge from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.21,0:17:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It might be because you were\Nagitated at that moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.08,0:17:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Power can be affected by emotions.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.25,0:17:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But if that wasn't the cause...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.96,0:17:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It could be a sign of the power disappearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.17,0:17:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Disappearing power will have\Na surge of strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.25,0:17:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Is my power fading away?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.71,0:17:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,As the brain grows older,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.08,0:17:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,there could be signs of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.54,0:17:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But Yuito's condition is...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.17,0:17:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito's brain has been\Nunder all sorts of damages.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.71,0:18:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Not to mention I was born a Bell Pepper.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.88,0:18:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.21,0:18:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You were a Bell Pepper?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.00,0:18:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You gained your power after the experiment.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.67,0:18:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Even you were once a Bell Pepper.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.17,0:18:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.38,0:18:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not entirely certain,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.42,0:18:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,but after listening to Luka's stories\Nabout him and his brother,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.29,0:18:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like I was once powerless too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.38,0:18:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That could be true.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.92,0:18:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,How long will my power last?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.75,0:18:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Will I start seeing anomalies in\Nthe next few days?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.71,0:18:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I doubt it would happen so quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.46,0:18:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,There haven't been a lot of recorded cases.\NI can't be too sure either.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.33,0:18:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,So, we don't know for sure what might happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.79,0:18:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's not draw any conclusion right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.75,0:18:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.04,0:18:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Our priority is to reach Togetsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.00,0:19:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.13,0:19:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take point and welcome you there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.71,0:19:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. We'll count on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.33,0:19:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,-It's open.\N-Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.83,0:19:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.25,0:19:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The enemies know we've infiltrated the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.75,0:19:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Go straight toward BABE.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.83,0:19:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,They are here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.96,0:19:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,They are well-prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.21,0:19:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Breakthrough their ranks.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.92,0:20:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito! Kasane!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.04,0:20:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The enemies really want their brains.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.83,0:20:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll use my teleportation.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.42,0:20:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Gather around now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.71,0:20:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,-Luka...\N-Are you going to teleport to BABE?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.29,0:20:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that a little too risky?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.00,0:20:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I've confirmed the layout
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.63,0:20:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,of this building when we last came.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.83,0:20:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as we are near BABE,\Nthey won't risk attacking us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.38,0:20:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito, hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.79,0:20:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.79,0:20:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Luka, begin now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.88,0:20:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Here I go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.42,0:20:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.71,0:21:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I think we've reached BABE safely.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.17,0:21:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It went well.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.46,0:21:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,How are you feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.33,0:21:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You need some rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.83,0:21:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,No. Thank you for your concern.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.92,0:21:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We should get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.42,0:21:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruka, Wataru.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.54,0:21:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Psynet connection has been shut down in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.29,0:21:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.13,0:21:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,This is stronger than the earthquake just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.71,0:21:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this caused by the Kunad Gate as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.21,0:21:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.88,0:21:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.50,0:21:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Please hear me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.04,0:22:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,This voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.17,0:22:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.13,0:22:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Please hear me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.13,0:22:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,-Mother!\N-Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.00,0:22:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,♫I'm troubled by my own yearning♫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.50,0:22:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Unveil the blocked sun ray♫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.42,0:22:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,♫There's a stranger in me♫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.50,0:22:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,♫That I've never seen♫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.04,0:22:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,♫I can not soar in the sky without fear♫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.96,0:22:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,♫I'm spreading my wings♫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.13,0:22:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Dancing gracefully like a bird♫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.46,0:23:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,♫And gazing towards the scarlet sky♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.08,0:23:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,♫I chased after the gust♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.42,0:23:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,♫The scenery spreads into\Nthe ever-changing world♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.67,0:23:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Inside the intertwined brilliance♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.00,0:23:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,♫I'm still searching for tomorrow's direction♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.04,0:23:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Tomorrow's in your hands♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.50,0:23:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Don't tell me now you're afraid♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.79,0:23:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,♫There's no time to waste♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.29,0:23:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Go forward♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.46,0:23:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Have no fear for anything♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.79,0:23:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Now, let's go♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.25,0:23:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Into a brand new day♫
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.38,0:24:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,REUNION
